                                                    Confirmation
                                                </h5>
                                                <p style="margin-bottom: 3px;font-weight:bold">Booking Status:
                                                    <span t-field="doc.state"/>
                                                </p>
                                                <h4 t-field="doc.hotel_id" style="margin-bottom: 3px;"/>
                                                <p style="margin-bottom: 3px; color: #455360;">
                                                    <span t-field="doc.hotel_id.address"/>
                                                </p>
                                            </div>
                                        </td>
                                    </tr>
                                </table>
                            </div>
                            <small>
                                <!--                                Dear Sir,-->
                                <!--                                <br/>-->
                                Thank you for choosing [<span t-field="doc.hotel_id"/>]
                                for your stay. We are delighted to welcome you and hope you have a memorable experience
                                with us. We look forward to hosting you and ensuring your visit is comfortable and
                                enjoyable.
                                <br/>
                                <!--                                يسرنا في فندق-->
                                <!--                                <span t-field="doc.hotel_id"/>,-->
